ComicInfo.Summary:
Sorry, I'm Not Ready to Die!: Walter Jamison's horoscope says one of his enemies will kill him tonight, so he gathers his enemies and confines them in his house where he can stop them.
Act of Vengeance: Raoul Boldin's brother asks him to kill the man responsible for his execution.
Grave in the Sky: Ruthless oil men scam a village into letting them drill but the village elder calls down the wrath of the local volcano.
